item.title: Thanks alot "safe zone TUT"
item.dc:creator: @hidendra Hidendra
item.description:
@hidendra wrote:

Let’s see, read your first error, you’re using a else block without first using if.
Secondly, that block is either in the wrong place or a parenthesis missing.

Thirdly, heightLevel ==1) isn’t a statement on its own, it has to be used, with for example in conjunction with an if statement.
Ditto to the fourth error, except it shouldn’t have semi-colon.
Fifthly, you’re using else without if.

Basically you just read the error, go to the line and see what you did wrong.
